被告人马卡洛归案后协助公安机关抓获同案被告人，有立功表现，可以从轻处罚。 被告人基芬达犯罪以后自动投案，如实供述自己的罪行，是自首，可以从轻处罚。被告人马卡洛、查马、贝纳德到案后如实供述自己的罪行，可以从轻处罚。四被告人自愿认罪认罚，可以依法从宽处理。 3 月 18 日，镇江中院作出一审判决，四被告人均被判犯盗窃罪，马卡洛被判处罚金 2000 元，其余三被告人各被判处罚金 1500 元；责令四被告人继续退赔盗窃物品折价款人民币 770.97 元。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-95744bba998ec2e2eb38d828048d1944_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452810851"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxvyvubO6/pgqEAMaCDYyOTA0MjE1IK+ApIMGMCw4mAxAJXIJNDUyODEwODUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1617587845.1242156", "card_id": "Q_28484672", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 5573}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何辨认身边的聪明人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a866633e5cbdcb59f0e83a72e1e39840_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/28484672"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxvyvubO6/pgqEAMaBzM1NzY2NTEgjrnUpwUwwAE4hp4MQCZyCDI4NDg0NjcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1617587845.1246548", "card_id": "Q_415082238", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 786}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家怎么评价刘浩存的颜值？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-85477940819c205e83df8735b621754a_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/415082238"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxvyvubO6/pgqEAMaCDU0NTE3ODk2IL7k6vkFMDs42A9AJ3IJNDE1MDgyMjM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1617587845.125